Alembic migrations for PolyFlow.

The database URL is taken from app.config.settings (POLYFLOW_DATABASE_URL).

Common commands:
    alembic upgrade head                 # apply all migrations
    alembic revision --autogenerate -m "msg"   # generate a new migration
    alembic downgrade -1                 # roll back one revision

The initial migration in versions/ creates the full schema. In docker, the API
container runs `alembic upgrade head` on startup (see entrypoint.sh).
